HOTA IND MFG CO said unconsolidated sales
in May rose 38.44% to NT$287,359,000 from NT$207,568,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            287,359          207,568    
YOY%              38.44%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,419,590        1,027,333   
YOY%              38.18% 
=================================================================
 